<subSubSection pageId="15" pageNumber="1018" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="15.[168,776,744,1427]" pageId="15" pageNumber="1018">
Epiphyte, native with distribution in the Southern Cone Region of South America. Vulnerable for reasons unknown (
<bibRefCitation author="Delucchi G" box="[281,444,901,925]" pageId="15" pageNumber="1018" pagination="19 - 31" refId="ref30263" refString="Delucchi G (2006) Las especies vegetales amenazadas de la Provincia de Buenos Aires: una actualizacion. Aprona Boletin Cientifico 39: 19 - 31." type="journal article" year="2006">Delucchi 2006</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<caption box="[813,1350,920,940]" pageId="15" pageNumber="1018" startId="15.[813,875,920,940]" targetBox="[813,1420,582,896]" targetPageId="15">
<paragraph blockId="15.[813,1350,920,940]" box="[813,1350,920,940]" pageId="15" pageNumber="1018">
